# Sample Tools Placeholder

This directory is where you can add your MCP server tools.

To create a new tool, add a class that implements the MCP tool patterns. See the documentation for examples.

Example:
```csharp
using ModelContextProtocol.Server;
using System.ComponentModel;

[McpServerToolType]
public sealed class MyTool
{
    [McpServerTool(Name = "my_tool")]
    [Description("Description of what my tool does")]
    public async Task<MyResponse> ExecuteAsync(
        [Description("Parameter description")] string input,
        CancellationToken cancellationToken = default)
    {
        // Implementation
    }
}
```
